on\\n{\\n  \\\"hooks\\\": true,\\n  \\\"transcript_analyzer\\\": true,\\n  \\\"transcript_preparer\\\": false,\\n  \\\"token_calculator\\\": false,\\n  \\\"text_generator\\\": false,\\n  \\\"hook_response_writer\\\": false,\\n  \\\"subagent_aware_extractor\\\": false\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Reimplemented dependencies (~200 lines total):**\\n- `repoRoot()` -> reads `ENTIRE_REPO_ROOT` env var, falls back to `git rev-parse --show-toplevel`\\n- `chunkJSONL`/`reassembleJSONL` -> copy from `cmd/entire/cli/agent/chunking.go:73-118`\\n- `stripIDEContextTags` -> copy regex logic from `cmd/entire/cli/textutil/ide_tags.go`\\n- Transcript parsing -> copy from `cmd/entire/cli/transcript/parse.go`\\n- `marshalIndentWithNewline` -> copy from `cmd/entire/cli/jsonutil/json.go`\\n- Logging -> simple `fmt.Fprintf(os.Stderr, ...)` instead of structured logging\\n\\n**`parse-hook` event mapping** (from `lifecycle.go`):\\n- `session-start` -> type 1 (SessionStart)\\n- `before-submit-prompt` -> type 2 (TurnStart), includes prompt/model\\n- `stop` -> type 3 (TurnEnd)\\n- `pre-compact` -> type 4 (Compaction)\\n- `session-end` -> type 5 (SessionEnd)\\n- `subagent-start` -> type 6 (SubagentStart), filtered on non-empty Task\\n- `subagent-stop` -> type 7 (SubagentEnd), filtered on non-empty Task\\n\\n**`extract-modified-files`:** Returns `{\\\"files\\\": null, \\\"current_position\\\": 0}` (Cursor transcripts lack tool_use blocks).\\n\\n## Files to Remove\\n\\n- **Delete** `cmd/entire/cli/agent/cursor/` (entire directory - cursor.go, hooks.go, lifecycle.go, transcript.go, types.go, AGENT.md, and all test files)\\n\\n## Files to Modify\\n\\n1. **`cmd/entire/cli/hooks_cmd.go`**: Remove `_ \\\"github.com/entireio/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/cursor\\\"` import. The cursor agent will be discovered via `external.DiscoverAndRegister()` which already runs on line 29.\\n\\n2. **`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation_test.go`**: Remove `_ \\\"github.com/entireio/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/cursor\\\"` i